Anambra State Governor, Willie Obiano, has appointed Nollywood actor Zubby Micheal as his Special Adviser on media. The actor announced the news on his Instagram page, where he shared a photo of himself holding what appeared to be his appointment letter. He wrote, “Dutycalls #SAonmedia #doings #nawedeyhere #blessup” he captioned the photos. Michael is a famous Nollywood actor, model, television personality and philanthropist, who is known for playing criminal, villain and hit man roles in movies. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.